{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Gamepad.index","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/index","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API\">Gamepad API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/axes\"><code>axes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/buttons\"><code>buttons</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/connected\"><code>connected</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>displayId</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/hand\"><code>hand</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/hapticActuators\"><code>hapticActuators</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><em><code>index</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/mapping\"><code>mapping</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/pose\"><code>pose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/vibrationActuator\"><code>vibrationActuator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Gamepad API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\"><code>GamepadButton</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a> インターフェイスの <code><strong>Gamepad.index</strong></code> プロパティは、現在システムに接続されているそれぞれの機器の整数の固有番号 (自動更新) の整数を返します。</p>\n\n<p>これは複数のコントローラーを識別するために使用することができます。接続が解除された後で再接続されたゲームパッドは、同じ番号を保持します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><span class=\"idlInterface\" id=\"idl-def-Gamepad\"><span class=\"idlAttribute\">readonly    attribute <span class=\"idlAttrType\">long</span>                <span class=\"idlAttrName\">index</span>;</span></span></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"gamepadconnected\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> gp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getGamepads</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  gamepadInfo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Gamepad connected at index \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> gp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>index <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\": \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> gp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>number</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"speicifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/#widl-Gamepad-index\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad<br><small lang=\"ja\">Gamepad.index の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Gamepad.index","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/index/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja